Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Domestic affairs
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brl0
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 8 Jan 1978
President Carter may discover his foreign policy ambitions have left domestic duties undone. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less